_357_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞不清楚的是你。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在拉特蘭的黎博利，自顧自地將拉特蘭戒律奉為圭臬，自顧自地將“拉特蘭教”視為信仰，自顧自地......把薩科塔視為神跡！", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃械、戒律、光環、共感......", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算這是薩科塔的神跡，與拉特蘭黎博利又有什麼關係？", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黎博利為何要信仰絕不會降臨於己身的神跡？！", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭的一切，拉特蘭教的一切，只屬於薩科塔，你還不明白嗎，菲亞梅塔！", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當真以為，自己成了他們的一分子嗎？", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#3$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i16", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0